        {
            "date": "2009-12-02 16:37:40", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I can not stress enough how important this feature is! ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " The difference will slap you  in the face when you access a site like Google Maps. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Where map scrolling is jerky on  Chrome and other current browsers, the Direct2D preview build of Firefox scrolls the  map EXTREMELY smooth.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "In fact, I can even maximize the window, switch to Satellite view (with labels), \n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "check all the boxes under \"More,\" and the map STILL scrolls extremely smooth. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Try  that with Chrome and it will choke, especially at a high resolution like 1920x1200.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "GPU-accelerated page rendering is the future, and I promise I will switch to the  first browser that puts out a stable release with it. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " I really love Chrome though. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "  I have been with Chrome since it was first released and I would really hate to leave  it. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " PLEASE start working on this feature!\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "/u/jrlogue/", 
            "email": "/u/jrlogue/"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2009-12-02 16:43:13", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Please don't begin making impassioned pleas on this bug. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Adding noise just makes it  less likely for us to look into this.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "We've already filed the bug. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " We already have plans to hardware-accelerate our  pipeline. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " We're always interested in improving speed, and this isn't flying under  our radar.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It will take some time to adapt our sandboxed rendering system to be able to use  tools like this.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "/u/pkasting@chromium.org/", 
            "email": "/u/pkasting@chromium.org/"
        }, 
